\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did your mother have anyone helping her in the house with the housework at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 What about your elder sisters. When you were a child, had they left home by then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 So there was no older daughter to help her with her work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you ever help her at all with the house work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, I'd do what I could, and get the wood and coal in, and help in, up in the woods, and get the wood, see, and bring it home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Were you expected to do it, or did you do it from your own choice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, I \{BLANK\} do it on m
e own, 'cause me mother she'd come up and, and get summat when we was getting short then she did show me where to get it from and that, 'cause we never had far to go, see ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 To get the wood?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 In the woods, 'cause it's a big woods, it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And you got all your wood from there, did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 What about cleaning, did you do any cleaning for her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 I would help do it. She did show me how to dust (?)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 I suppose you were the only one at home, the only child at home for a long period.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And your father, did he help, did he do any housework?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Not but very little, he had the garden to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And, of course, hours were so long then, weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, and (..) \{BLANK\} when they got, older. I (..) did a main bit of gardening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 
When you were a little boy, about as old as your little great grandchild, there, do you remember your father putting you to bed or telling you stories, or doing anything for you at all, or did your mother do all that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Sometimes one, and sometimes the other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 He did do things like the mothering sort of things, did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, I (he) told me (?) where (he'd) been doing during the day or anything like that, where he'd, where he'd been to
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 He talked to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did he ever take you out on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 What sort of places would you go to?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, we, we had a, he had a S-, Sunday off, and I and him and got some other fellows see with a
 pony and trap from, take us right down to (..)? \{BLANK\} and back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Just you, or did your mother go too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, only, only we three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 His friend, you mean, and you and him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you enjoy that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did he do anything like decorating in the house or mending things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Nothing hardly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 What about things like washing up and making fires and cooking? Did he ever have occasion to ..?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes he might help with that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 He could cook, could he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When would he cook, for example?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 M-, mo-, more of a Sunday than any help out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Some}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14703675\charrsid7686223  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 
people have told me their fathers used to do the Sunday dinner. Did he do, help with that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 He would help out doing that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When your mother did the washing in her own home .. she did it at home I suppose?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did she do it one particular day, or just when ..?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, had to go according to the weather.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 She didn't always do it the same day every week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Ah, no, 'cause she was out at washing, see, a couple of days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 
When she did the cleaning of her rooms, did she have a routine so that she did one room one day, and one another, or did she just fit it in as ..?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 (..) \{BLANK\} She'd fit it in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When you were a child, you said, you had to be in by nine or ten. Was it nine or ..?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, oh, ten (?) it was mostly, well, all, it all depends on the, the time of year as well, well in the summer time (..) \{BLANK\}
 all hours, as we had to make hay while the sun did shine, as the saying is.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You were making hay, weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Working long hours, but in ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 But in the winter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, we were very often in bed at eight o'clock 'cause got to get up early, see, mornings, 'cause I had a, I had two mile to walk to scho
ol.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 I remember you said that you found your way by the little paths?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Ah.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When you were a little boy, did your mother put you to bed, or did you put yourself to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 I'd go to bed myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 In those days, people have told me that they used to have one bath night a week. Did you have that system in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, I, I, on, once a week, yes, and that was a galvanized bath then, in front the fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did she heat the water on her paraffin stove?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no, we didn't have no paraffin(?) (..) \{BLANK\} we had a (..) \{ILLEGIBLE\}
 what we did call (..) in the back kitchen where we did, where she did do the washing, and not only that, she did do, m-, make her own bread, 'cause we had the baking oven, join-, joining the boiler in the back kitchen.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was the back kitchen attached to the house, or was it like a wash-house, separate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, it was attached to, sort of a lean-to, like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When you had your bath, was it always the same night of the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, n-, near enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 What night would it usually be, then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 
Well, Saturday, and also Sunday, all depends upon the time of the year, see, it was in the summer time, well, it would be rather late nights, by, by, un-, unless we was(n't) haymaking or anything, or (..) \{BLANK\} cutting, or (..) \{BLANK\}
 like that. If we wasn't doing that, well, it was on a Saturday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Otherwise it might be a Sunday night, might it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you have clean clothes on once a week, when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 After the bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 That's it, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 
I wanted to ask you about meals in those days, because people say that customs have changed quite a lot, with food, not all the foods that they have now. Where did you eat your meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 In that kitchen where the stove was, was that the one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, where the, where the grate was.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 I see, you had a kitchen where you eat, and a kitchen where the stove was, separate, was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 We never had no stove, not then, no we had to do all (..) on the fire ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 On the grate, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, and there was a oven, see, under, I-, in the grate, see, where you could put the coal under and see for to hot, hot it up
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And then you also had one where you did the bread. Was that another one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 There wasn't any front room in that house, there wouldn't have been the room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 So you always eat in that same room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you have a breakfast in the morning, before you ..?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Can you remember what you used to eat in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 
Oh, sometimes, was, er, a boiled egg and bread and butter, or, s-, bread and butter and jam, that's what I liked and, er, also bit of toast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No porridge in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 (..) \{BLANK\} Quaker Oats, if anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 But not regularly, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Ah, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you ever have milk to drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 How often would you have a glass of milk, do you think? because people tell me they had less then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, I couldn't say exact, but, I, I'd have some occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 It wasn't a regular thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 So when you were a child, a schoolboy, would you have tea in the mornings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, at me breakfast, and always (um, take our own?) some tea around lunch and dinner to school with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You'd take your lunch and dinner with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 What would you take by way of lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, a piece of bread and butter, then dinner perhaps a bit of bread and cheese.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When you had your breakfast, was your father and mother with you, or did you have it on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, they was there, one or the other was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And would your father sometimes have gone out earlier?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, milking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When he went out earlier, would he come back for breakfast, or did he take something with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, he didn't come back to breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When your sisters were away, I think you said one or more was in service when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did they come home sometimes for holidays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was no holidays then, they di
d come home occasionally, or else, or else, we did go and see them. I did mostly, no matter where where she was at service, I did, I did always find me way there.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was she usually in this part of the country, or sometimes further away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no (?) al-, always this part of the country, but you might say between here, Old Sodbury and, er, Cherrifield.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When you had your midday dinner, did your mother have a hot dinner midday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Not as a regular thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no, mostly nights.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Because you'd take your sandwiches with you, wouldn't you ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And did your father do the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 A-, a-, all depends upon where he was at work. If he was handy he'd have it home, if it was a distance away, well, he'd take it with him.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And if he had it at home, what would your mother cook then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, summat of all sorts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Could you tell me, for example, what things she might cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, \{BLANK\} 'taters and cabbage and carrots or anything like that, all depends the time of the year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 What there was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, and a bit of meat of some sort.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 I remember you said you used to get the rabbits from poaching ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 A lot of the farm people had to do that, didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 How often could your mother afford to buy meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Not very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Would there be periods of, say, weeks when she would be dependent on the rabbits, or would she go to the butcher every week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Ah, no, well, she, 'twas such a distance to go, see, my dear, you see, \{BLANK\}
 you might say, if we wanted anything extra, we had to come to Sodbury, well, it was four mile each way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 So she wouldn't go every week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Ah, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And the butcher didn't call then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Not very often. If we wa
nted him, well, we did, er, we (..) did take the message to the farm, see, and they can tell him for to bring summat or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You know how nowadays, if people have vegetables, they always expect to have meat too ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 In those days it wasn't like that, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Your father might come home and have potatoes and carrots, and he wouldn't expect to have meat as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Just the vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Unless there was, what we did all like was a, a nice big piece of bacon, boil it ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was that your own pig that you kept?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And you did all that yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you ever keep a pig for selling when you fattened it up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No, well, if, if we did we did have a part on him back, as you might say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You kept a part back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 In the evening, did you come home for tea from school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was that when your mother usually cooked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did your father come back then too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And what sort of food would she cook then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, 'taters and cabbage and, well, all depends what other vegetables there was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you ever have salad at all in the summer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Not much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 I think you said you used to have poultry in your own home when you were married ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 .. did your father have poultry too, your father and mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No, never had the room, not there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 So, did they ever have eggs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, we could, we could always get plenty eggs on the farm cheap.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 So she used to cook eggs sometimes, did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 I remember you said for breakfast, and did she ever make puddings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When would you usually have them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Mostly of a Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 What type?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, it's the sort what we did always like, spotted dog.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 With currants in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes. Boiled
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did she ever make a fruit tart, or didn't they have fruit trees?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, we, er, we had currants and gooseberries and all, and plums and that, there, see
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 So they grew their own vegetables and fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did they ever need to buy any, or did they get enough from what they grew?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, we'd buy some occasionally ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 But most of the time ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, we'd have our own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And you didn't have any room for keeping your own livestock, then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No. (..) \{BLANK\} that'd be the front lawn, see (??) well we did (..) bottle a lot besides making jam (..) as that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You had bottled fruit, did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, then, er, we had summat for to (..) tide us over, see, when, in the winter time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 
When you were a child, did you all eat the same food? Some people have told me that their mothers used to go short because there wasn't enough. Was it like that in your family?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Because there weren't so many children at home, I suppose, that's why.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, \{BLANK\} yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And your father, did he have the same, or did he have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no, all about the same, well, in fact, I didn't eat so much as some on them, not then, still (..) the food was good then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You think so?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was grace ever said at meals at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Were you allowed to talk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Could you choose what you wanted to eat, or did you accept everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, might ask me what I should like, and I did say, if it wasn't there, I had to put up with what there was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 If your mother cooked something and you didn't feel like it, you wouldn't have to eat it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And if she offered you some cabbage and you took some on your plate, and then you didn't finish it, what would she say to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, her wouldn't say nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 She wasn't fussy in that way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Could you ask for a second helping if you wanted some more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, yes, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was she particular how you sat and how you held your knife and fork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 She wouldn't mind if you put your elbows on the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you ever bring a toy, when you were a little boy, to the table or a book?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, we never had such things, they was luxuries.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Could you get down from the table when you wanted to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You didn't all have to wait to finish together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was your mother an easy going person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes, very.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was she a motherly kind of woman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 If you were worried about something, who would you take your worries to, would it be your mother or your father, or both of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, I should, I should, um, tell mother first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And she was easy to talk to, was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When the meal was served up, did she serve it from dishes on the table, or did she serve it separately?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, out of the saucepan.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Can you tell me how your mother and father expected you to behave at that time, because people say that times have changed in the way ..?

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, I was told for to behave myself and be honest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Be honest, that's what they emphasized, did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Aye, they believed in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 If, say, a boy hit you, and you told them, what would they say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, hit him back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 They'd tell you to defend yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did they ever have to tell you not to swear when you were a child? Did they have any feelings about language, or didn't they worry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No, there wasn't much of that said. They don't believe in that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 But it wasn't a problem you mean at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Maybe it's more in the towns, perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes. Everybody gets their ups and downs, I know, otherwise, I, I, I don't believe in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you ever have to be punished, or did you always do what they said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Very seldom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You were an obedient child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And if they did punish you what sort of punishment would they give you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Go off to bed without any supper, didn't have any tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You weren't ever caned by them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No hitting or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When they punished you, can you remember how you felt about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 I didn't cry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Do you remember if you felt angry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 These ideas yo
u told me, you were brought up to believe in honesty and that kind of thing. Did you get that more from your mother or more from your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Both of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 They both took a hand in your upbringing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Can you remember if there were any musical instruments in your home, a piano or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, no, we had a, the old man as was a lodger 'long with us, he had a v-, violin.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And did he play it to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes. When he died a farmer down in the village bought it
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You didn't learn to play yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And did you sing, or your mother sing at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, I did mostly s-, sing a few songs what I'd learned at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 But you didn't gather round when he played the violin and sing, or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, you mi-, you might say wasn't old enough, see, for to understand all that and ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did your parents ever play any games with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Very seldom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you have draughts, or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, that wasn't thought of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 They did talk to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Some people have said that their mother and father didn't talk to them at that time, but they did talk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you have anything to read in the house or was that out of the question, any newspaper, or ..?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 
Oh, yes, we had a newspaper, and I, I had to read that, see, all the bits and pieces, you might say, 'cause neither on 'em couldn't, couldn't read nor write. I had to do that myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 So would you read aloud to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you ever have any family prayers at that time? I remember you said you used to go to prayer meetings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, that was at different farms during the winter months. Well, the vicar, he'd come, come, com
e in, in a certain nights, see, well, we did (..) we did go to church, Sundays, and he did he did speak out in church where 'a' was going, and where, when, whereabouts and what time, and we did always go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 But you didn't have prayers aloud just in your own family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 It was organised by the vicar?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When you were a small child, a schoolboy, do you remember a funeral in the family, that you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 The only, the only one as I can remember in me school days was the old man as lodged along with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 He died while he was lodging did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Can you remember what it was like, the funeral, where there a lot of people there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Ah, no, nobody hardly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 He didn't have many people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you have a funeral tea afterwards, or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 
I remember you said how you used to go out with your father in the pony and trap, did you, I don't suppose you ever went away for a holiday, because they didn't have them, really then, did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You never went and spent a night anywhere else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you ever go out shopping with your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Where would you go for shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, if we wanted anything extra, 'twas, we, er, we
'd go down to Wickwar that's through the woods, or else come over here to Sodbury. We did, we did occasionally go up to Hawkesbury
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And that five shilling suit you said you bought with the money the farmer gave you, where was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 We came over to Sodbury, to John Morgan's where, where Jack Sandals is today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you buy that on your own or did your mother help you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, oh, no I buy it on me own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Going shopping for clothes, did you do that every year or more often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no, all depends upon when (..) I for to get any money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 But you bought your clothes out of your own money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did they have bank holidays then you went out on outings for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Only with the s-, with the school, the, the Sunday School.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 A Sunday School outing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 That's when you went to Weston?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Were Saturdays any different in those days? You didn't go to school. Did you work all day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 How old were you when you first started working for the farmer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, about, er, seven or eight. That was carrying the straw for to do the thatching.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When you did that, can you remember what the first money you got for working for him was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, his mother, see, had always given me dinner and tea.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 That was the payment, was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, that was part of it. He might give me a shilling or two (..) in and out
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 But you didn't get a regular sum every week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no, oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You said your parents used to attend church? Did they both go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did they go regularly or occasionally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no, not regularly, only occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 But did you go to Sunday School regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Were there any social activities to do with the church that you used to take part in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No there was nothing, nothing going on then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No socials, or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And was there a Band of Hope or Temperance Club of any kind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No. The only thing as I, done after I left school, I did ring the bells, ring the old year out and new one in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And the evening classes where you learnt carpentry, were those attached to the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no, that was you might say evening cla-, class through the schoolmaster as came there after I'd le
ft school. It was 'bout a dozen of us attended that, that evening class.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 That was after you'd left school that you went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 How long did you go for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 'Bout two ye-, two year I think 'twas after I, after I'd left school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 How often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, t-, twice a week I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was it just carpentry you learnt?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no, we had, er, er, estimating different, er, different places by the road signs (???)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And a, a bit of, little bit of 'rithmetic, adding up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you enjoy going?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, they did bring back memories of school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Because of course you were so young when you left school those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, I was thirteen, and I got me school leaving certificate here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 What standard did you pass?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Up in, well, s-, six, I believe it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When you were a child, did your parents take an interest in politics at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 They didn't discuss politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Do you know if they voted, your father, women wouldn't have had a vote?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, if 'a' did, er, perhaps two or three of them'd go together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 
At that time a lot of men, I think this was particularly true in the country areas, people have told me, they often felt they risked their job if they voted, perhaps, they didn't vote the way their employer would like them to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Do you remember people talking about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, some of them would ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Feel they must vote a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was that true of your father, do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Ah, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 There wasn't pressure on him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Were his views more to the Conservative or more to the Labour side do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Well, tell you the truth, I couldn't say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You just don't know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 But they weren't active in politics, or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Were you yourself political ..?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes in me, in me older days.
