\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No. \{BLANK\} where it was on the farm, see, over there he always had plenty of beer and cider for to drink.
