\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You were saying your father was born in Hawkesbury.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
