Oh, there wasn't much of that to be done in them days, and all the washing you had to do 'em by hand. No washing machines or wringers or anything, well we did have, I did get a wringer for to help her out see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You got her a wringer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Can you think of anything else you used to do with the children? When they were little, for example, did you ever feed them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes. yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You'd do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Were there any things you didn't like doing for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Not as I know of. I'd do anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Even change them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 It's very interesting because .. Do you think when you took the children out in t
he pram, was that a usual thing to do, did other people do that too?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Sometimes, me brother-in-law did occasionally, they, they only had two, and \{BLANK\}
 see, his, his youngest didn't know when the, when the water did boil had to come down and ask mine, and used to come up and show her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 It's funny the things you take for granted, which you have to learn.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you continue having the weekly bath, like you'd had in your own home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did you bath the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, I did if she, if Nan was out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was she quite often out in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no, only, only occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And if she was in did you give her a hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, yes, 'cause we had to hot, we'd hot the water, see, in the boiler.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 So it was quite a job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 
Oh, yes, 'cause the boiler was just inside the d-, just inside the front door, as you might say, what, what a lot on 'em'd call in the hall, or what we'd call then in the passage, and, and we, I had to car-, carry it all me own, all, all me (..) \{BLANK\}
 especially, from the farm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, of course, because there were no taps in the farm area.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no, and (..) \{BLANK\} we had a, we had a pond, see, where I did get the water for washing or swilling down, aren't much of that done
 today, swilling down, after washing and that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 What is that exactly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Ooh, (..) Pour a lot of water down and, and, and get your broom to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, because there'd be a mess on the floor, you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 How often did you fetch the water, then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, every, every day for washing, for drinking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You fetched it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did she ever fetch water?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 No, because it's heavy, isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes, 'cause well I had near, what, 150 yards to carry it, and a short cut at that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 That's a long way to carry water.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 
Yes, and I know on one, on one occasion, well, I had a, I had a surprise. We had a dry time, then come a lot of rain, and when we were waiting for to get a drink of water, for to have a drink myself i
n a glass, well, when I got it out the tap, well, it was a case of throwing it away, 'cause the reason why, well the water from the coal yard and the lavatory, well, 'twas open (?) (..) drain. Had to sink (?) back into the well, 'cause the well wasn't abo
ve ten yards away from}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11999753\charrsid7686223  i}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 t.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 You might have got very ill if you hadn't realized.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Aye. (..) \{BLANK\} us, us, us a warning (..) \{BLANK\}
 I never had none (..) Day after, I went up (..) to my brother in law's and got it (..); Had to walk a bit further bu
t I didn't mind about that, long as I had some decent (..) stuff I'd rather have it out, out the little pond and that was land drainage water that would have been.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Did your brother in law live quite close?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes. Somewhere, somewhere (..) on the same distance. Little bit farther of the two (?)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was that your wife's sister's husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 
Yes. Oh, I and he worked together, for over twenty year, nineteen year on the one farm and I worked along with, him on other farm (..) along as before I had to go in the army.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 And did she, that would be your sister in law ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 .. did she and your wife help each other out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes. yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 What sort of things did they do for each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When they were having, having babies, see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 That was the sister you mentioned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 
Yes. (..) Although there was another person, see, as, as lived next door, then there was, that was one house in two, joining one another, then there was a little cottage close by, well, they come and help out any time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Were they related too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Ah, no, they was no relation, see, but they, they had a family well, three on 'em, but then they was, they was (..) \{BLANK\}
 my age and older, 'cause we went to school together for ..
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 I forgot to ask you, when you married your wife, her mother had passed on, hadn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was her father still alive?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 When you wanted to marry her, did you go and ask her father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Oh, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8593187 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Was that the custom then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13439349 S  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15617501\charrsid7686223 Yes. "Cause she wasn't of age, see (..) \{BLANK\} and he had to sign the form.
